caption: Raspberry
description:
Raspberries are often found along the edges of large open meadows.
Raspberries are valuable in both early game as a basic food item and in mid-late game as a necessary ingredient for the early-tier Queens jam and the Medium healing mead. Thus, gathering raspberries when encountered is usually valuable.

caption: Mushroom
description: Mushroom can be found on the ground in the Meadows, Black Forest and Swamp. Picked mushrooms will respawn after 240 minutes at the same place that they were picked. Unlike the case with raspberries and blueberries, which do not return if the plant itself is removed, mushrooms will return if the ground is cleared or even excavated.

caption: Boar meat
description: Boar meat is a basic food source, it can be found by killing Boars.
